description:
The rare REH guitar instructional PART 2 video by Pat Martino circa 1994. This is the Russian version, so it's overdubbed, but you can hear Pat under it for the most part. Better than nothing!

Here's what appears to be the accompanying tab and music files for Part 1 and Part 2 of this video series.

https://www.mediafire.com/file/dvo46zrkdii1rbd/Pat_Martino-Creative_Force_-_Part1_-_Part_2_-_%28Guitar_Book_+_CD%29.zip/file
